    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.1",
          "pli": "“‘Bhayan’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, ‘danger’ is a term for sensual pleasures. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.2",
          "pli": "‘Dukkhan’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘Suffering’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.3",
          "pli": "‘Rogo’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘disease’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.4",
          "pli": "‘Gaṇḍo’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘boil’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.5",
          "pli": "‘Sallan’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘dart’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.6",
          "pli": "‘Saṅgo’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘tie’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.7",
          "pli": "‘Paṅko’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "‘bog’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.8",
          "pli": "‘Gabbho’ti, bhikkhave, kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "and ‘womb’ are terms for sensual pleasures. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.9",
          "pli": "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, ‘bhayan’ti kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ? ",
          "en": "And why is ‘danger’ a term for sensual pleasures? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.10",
          "pli": "Yasmā ca kāmarāgarattāyaṃ, bhikkhave, chandarāgavinibaddho diṭṭhadhammikāpi bhayā na parimuccati, samparāyikāpi bhayā na parimuccati, tasmā ‘bhayan’ti kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "Someone who is caught up in sensual greed and shackled by lustful desire is not freed from dangers in the present life or in lives to come. That is why ‘danger’ is a term for sensual pleasures. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.11",
          "pli": "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, ‘dukkhan’ti … pe … ",
          "en": "And why are ‘suffering’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.12",
          "pli": "‘rogo’ti … ",
          "en": "‘disease’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.13",
          "pli": "‘gaṇḍo’ti … ",
          "en": "‘boil’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.14",
          "pli": "‘sallan’ti … ",
          "en": "‘dart’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.15",
          "pli": "‘saṅgo’ti … ",
          "en": "‘tie’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.16",
          "pli": "‘paṅko’ti … ",
          "en": "‘bog’, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.17",
          "pli": "‘gabbho’ti kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ? ",
          "en": "and ‘womb’ terms for sensual pleasures? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:1.18",
          "pli": "Yasmā ca kāmarāgarattāyaṃ, bhikkhave, chandarāgavinibaddho diṭṭhadhammikāpi gabbhā na parimuccati, samparāyikāpi gabbhā na parimuccati, tasmā ‘gabbho’ti kāmānametaṃ adhivacanaṃ. ",
          "en": "Someone who is caught up in sensual greed and shackled by lustful desire is not freed from wombs in the present life or in lives to come. That is why ‘womb’ is a term for sensual pleasures. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:2.1",
          "pli": "Bhayaṃ dukkhañca rogo ca, ",
          "en": "Danger, suffering, and disease, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:2.2",
          "pli": "gaṇḍo sallañca saṅgo ca; ",
          "en": "boil, dart, and tie, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:2.3",
          "pli": "Paṅko gabbho ca ubhayaṃ, ",
          "en": "and bogs and wombs both. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:2.4",
          "pli": "ete kāmā pavuccanti; ",
          "en": "These describe the sensual pleasures "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:2.5",
          "pli": "Yattha satto puthujjano. ",
          "en": "to which ordinary people are attached. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:3.1",
          "pli": "Otiṇṇo sātarūpena, ",
          "en": "Swamped by things that seem pleasant, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:3.2",
          "pli": "puna gabbhāya gacchati; ",
          "en": "you go to another womb. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:3.3",
          "pli": "Yato ca bhikkhu ātāpī, ",
          "en": "But when a mendicant is keen, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:3.4",
          "pli": "sampajaññaṃ na riccati. ",
          "en": "and doesn’t forget awareness, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:4.1",
          "pli": "So imaṃ palipathaṃ duggaṃ, ",
          "en": "in this way they transcend "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:4.2",
          "pli": "atikkamma tathāvidho; ",
          "en": "this grueling swamp. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:4.3",
          "pli": "Pajaṃ jātijarūpetaṃ, ",
          "en": "They watch this population as it trembles, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:4.4",
          "pli": "phandamānaṃ avekkhatī”ti. ",
          "en": "fallen into rebirth and old age.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.56:4.5",
          "pli": "Chaṭṭhaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
